04 Jul 2013 03:40






This article is being placed up for review. Please check it out, I think it needs more attention.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

I feel like I really shouldn't like this, as it's quite silly and doesn't really hold up super well as an SCP article with the lolfoundation tone, but I'll be damned if I don't find it kind of charming. This really is the epitome of what an old SCP on editthis looked like, and it has some cool historical context. This was actually written on the old wiki to be a sort of counter for Josie, which I always thought was quite interesting. I've upvoted this for those reasons, and I love this one just the way it is. That being said, this is a fairly generic shapeshifter with a mildly amusing fart joke at the end, and it could definitely stand for something to make it juicier.

Side note, I love the picture.








Whether you like it or not, history is on our side. We will bury you!




